<item>
            <title>[PIG-421] error with complex nested plan</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-421</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Even after applying patch for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-398&quot; title=&quot;Expressions not allowed inside foreach&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-398&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-398&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, the following query still fails:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;a = load &apos;studenttab10k&apos; as (name, age, gpa);&lt;br/&gt;
b = filter a by age &amp;lt; 20;&lt;br/&gt;
c = group b by age;&lt;br/&gt;
d = foreach c &lt;/p&gt;
{
    cf = filter b by gpa &amp;lt; 3.0;
    cp = cf.gpa;
        cd = distinct cp;
    co = order cd by $0;
    generate group, flatten(co);
    }
&lt;p&gt;store d into &apos;output&apos;;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
